sequenceDiagram
    participant MO as Middle Office
    participant BO as BO (Integration API)
    participant SNS as SNS / EventBridge
    participant SQS as SQS (BOSI Queue)
    participant BOSI as BOSI Service
    participant SI as S&I Platform

    MO->>BO: New dossier with S&I account
    BO->>BO: Create Credit + Related Product<br/>+ calculate initial premium
    BO->>SNS: Publish credit.created event
    SNS->>SQS: Route via EventBridge rule
    SQS->>BOSI: Consume message
    Note over BOSI: Account Orchestrator
    BOSI->>BO: GET /api/v2/related-products/{id}
    BO-->>BOSI: Related Product details
    BOSI->>BO: GET /api/v2/parties/{partyId}
    BO-->>BOSI: Party details
    BOSI->>BO: GET /api/v2/loans/{creditId}
    BO-->>BOSI: Loan details (incl. premium)
    Note over BOSI: Transform to S&I format
    BOSI->>SI: POST /accounts
    SI-->>BOSI: 201 Created {accountId}
    Note over SQS: Delete message (ack)
